snippet.title: Fat Goblins Announcement Trailer! 2024!
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2450350/Fat_Goblins/

Prepare for goblin-packed, hat-stealing, and princess-fattening team based 16v16 combat! Siege the castle walls, rescue your pudgy princess, fatten up the enemy princess with delicious meat, unlock new hats & weapons, and kill each other repeatedly in silly and chaotic PvP war!

Fat Goblins will launch in early 2024!
